Happy one year anniversary to @thehollywoodreveal 💫 This week my little indie podcast baby was in the top 10 Apple chart in Portugal! And over the past few months has been in the top 50 Apple chart in the TV & Film Interview category, in the US, UK, Canada & Australia! I’m up against many big network podcasts, some belonging to those big studios we are striking against right now, I have no marketing budget & do it all from my bedroom. If you want to support me as an indie creative please go have a listen and leave a 5 star review, I’ll be so grateful! 
💛 Link in my bio or find it on all your favourite podcast places. Thank you to everyone that’s listened already & to all my incredible guests who inspire, entertain & motive me 🌟
